This paper is about improving the performance of neural machine translation systems by incorporating knowledge graphs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which includes papers on natural language processing and machine translation. The use of knowledge graphs also suggests that cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are likely categories. Additionally, the paper involves data management and information retrieval, which could place it in cs.DB (Databases) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval) categories.
